align=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Apologies and an explanation</span><hr size=1> For those of you who were in Sebilis today when I went off on Charm, I'm sorry you had to be witness to it. I realize some of you have bought or sold accounts, and I in no way meant to insult those of you who deserved none, so with that said allow me to explain my actions. Charm has been Ebayed more times than I can count on one hand, everyone knows this. I have a strong grudge versus Charm and anyone who purchases him simply because a large portion of his equipment at one time belonged to me and some friends when he ebayed out. Obviously we never saw it again. I have formed the opinions I have on ebayed characters from experience both in interacting and grouping with a good amount of them, and from horror stories I've heard from friends. From my experience a good portion of them are selfish and uncaring about their reputation, simply because they can ruin that persons name and then auction him off to buy a new character, not only suckering some poor guy/gal into buying an absolutely despised character without knowledge, but doing things considered illegal in game while they're at it (ninja looting, training, etc etc). Now PLEASE note there are obvious exceptions to this, and you know who you are, and there are a few people who I know are ebayed that I consider good and trustworthy friends, its just that those friends had to work twice as hard to prove themselves in my eyes due to a bias I have formed over the last year and a half of interacting with fools and asses.<br>
<br>
Again, please realize, there are exceptions to the statements above, and I am more than willing to reconcile problems with people who I angered. I am not above apologizing publicly for my harsh words, however there is a personal note carried within this message that the entire world does not need to see. I was disturbed to hear that the &quot;no&quot; votes for my membership jumped up to 3 after this incident and I wanted to resolve it before people got the wrong idea. If you have any question's or problems, please feel free to contact me in game as Utaelaelael, Hieya or Baritenor and I will address them.<br>
<br>
/salute Infinitus Vindicat<br>
<br>
Utaelaelael Soultaker 57th Defiler of Prexus<br>
Hieya Bewttodehead 51st Disciple of Prexus<br>
Baritenor Immatwink now 9th bard of Prexus <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/uhieya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hieya</A> at: 9/16/01 2:58:38 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/uninianeaurelianus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Niniane Aurelianus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/16/01 5:43:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=281.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Apologies and an explanation</span><hr size=1> While I respect that fact that you apologize, you still showed you true face. <br>
You acted in a way that represents everything I despise.<br>
<br>
The way you generalized today was just childish in the extreme.<br>
<br>
It would be like me saying, I have played with a lot of BAD necroes, you're a necro......<br>
<br>
This doesnt tell much about you but would tell a heck of a lot about me and my single mindedness.<br>
<br>
